00:08:23.380 --> 00:08:26.780
This is how the Mirror
API works.

00:08:26.780 --> 00:08:30.560
It's RESTful architecture.

00:08:30.560 --> 00:08:33.934
JSON is the payload encoding,
and OAuth

00:08:33.934 --> 00:08:35.299
is the install process.

